                <div><p style="line-height:15.6pt; margin:3.1pt 17.85pt 0pt 13.35pt; orphans:0; text-align:right; text-indent:-2.85pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.001.png" width="37" height="41" alt="" style="margin-left:413.25pt; margin-top:-1.25pt; position:absolute; z-index:-65526"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.002.png" width="248" height="34" alt="" style="margin-left:254.45pt; margin-top:-2.5pt; position:absolute; z-index:-131067"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.003.png" width="442" height="19" alt="" style="margin-left:-80.55pt; margin-top:3.7pt; position:absolute; z-index:-131068"><span style="color:#ffffff; font-family:方正粗倩简体; font-size:9pt">二维动画师</span><span style="color:#ffffff; font-family:方正粗倩简体; font-size:9pt">教程</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; widows:0"><span style="color:#e36c09; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:42pt; font-weight:bold">项目1</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:18pt; font-weight:bold">认识二维动画师</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">你是一个热爱二维动画的人，你不想再消费其他人的作品，你想要创造自己的二维动画世界。于是你想要进入二维动画行业，想要去应聘某个公司的二维动画师的岗位，所以你决定要先了解二维动画师……</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.004.jpeg" width="111" height="30" alt="大拇哥教育-电子教材-标签集 - 副本-43"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold"> 认识二维动画制作</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">我们要认识二维动画师，不能盲人摸象，要先整体后局部，因此我们首先要认识什么是二维动画制作。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.005.png" width="24" height="24" alt="标签集-20"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">相关知识</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.006.png" width="23" height="19" alt="标签集-08"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 什么是动画</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:18.4pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">从广义上来说，只要不是用实际拍摄的方法得到的运动影像都可以算是动画。简单地说，人工制作的动态视觉效果就是动画。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.007.png" width="23" height="19" alt="标签集-09"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 动画的类别</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">按照制作的方式区别动画可以分成两种，二维动画和三维动画。二维动画主要包括：传统手绘动画、剪纸动画、Flash动画、MG动画等，如图1-1~图1-4所示。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">&nbsp;</span></p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; margin-left:0pt"><tbody><tr><td style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.008.png" width="4" height="8" alt=""><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.008.png" width="4" height="8" alt=""></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.008.png" width="4" height="8" alt=""><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.009.jpeg" width="276" height="155" alt="瑞克和莫蒂"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-1美国手绘动画片《瑞克和莫蒂》</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">&nbsp;</span></p></td><td style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin: