1-05~图1-07所示。</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.013.jpeg" width="232" height="131" alt="小羊肖恩"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-5英国黏土动画片《小羊肖恩》</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p></td><td style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.014.jpeg" width="236" height="126" alt="僵尸新娘"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-6美国木偶动画片《僵尸新娘》</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.015.png" width="324" height="182" alt=""></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-7中国Maya动画片《小瑞与大魔王》</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-5~图1-7&nbsp; 三维动画</span></p></td></tr><!--[if !supportMisalignedColumns]><tr style="height:0pt"><td style="width:218.05pt; border:none"></td><td style="width:218.05pt; border:none"></td></tr><![endif]--></tbody></table><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.016.png" width="24" height="24" alt="标签集-20"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">任务分析 </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.017.png" width="23" height="19" alt="标签集-08"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">任务目的</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0.4pt; orphans:0; text-indent:17.95pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">1. 掌握二维动画的概念，了解二维动画与三维动画的区别；</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0.4pt; orphans:0; text-indent:17.95pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">2. 掌握二维动画制作流程的基础知识；</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 0.4pt; orphans:0; text-indent:17.95pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">3. 掌握制作二维动画岗位的基础知识。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.018.png" width="23" height="19" alt="标签集-09"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">实施思路</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">要认识二维动画制作，需要通过循序渐进的方法，从整体到局部地分步骤进行。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">1. 认识什么是二维动画</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">通过网络搜索或查找资料，了解二维动画的基本概念；通过观看二维动画片，直观地了解二维动画的特征；通过了解二维动画与三维动画的区别，更全面地了解二维动画的概念。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">2. 认识二维动画的制作流程</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">通过网络搜索或查找资料，全面认识三种不同的二维动画的制作流程。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">3. 认识制作二维动画的岗位</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">通过网络搜索或查找资料，全面认识三种不同的二维动画制作岗位。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.016.png" width="24" height="24" alt="标签集-20"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">任务实施 </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.017.png" width="23" height="19" alt="标签集-08"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 什么是二维动画</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.019.png" width="64" height="21" alt=""><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 二维动画的基本概念</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">我们打开搜索引擎，搜索”二维动画制作““什么是二维动画”等关键词，可以找到许多关于二维动画的资料，如图1-8所示。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">网络</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">对二维动画的解释：</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">”</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">二维画面是平面上的画面。纸张、照片或计算机屏幕显示，无论画面的立体感有多强，终究只是在二维空间上模拟真实的三维空间效果。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">”</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.020.png" width="219" height="328" alt=""></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-8搜索结果</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.021.png" width="64" height="21" alt=""><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 二维动画的特征</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">阅读图文资料，观看二维动画片，直观地了解二维动画的特征。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">例如：观看宫崎骏大师的动画电影，如图1-9所示。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.022.jpeg" width="405" height="228" alt="龙猫"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-9宫崎骏导演动画《龙猫》</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">通过这一步骤我们了解到二维动画有以下特征：</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">1. 二维动画由动画师通过手绘或者电脑绘制而成，有着明显的手绘痕迹，比如角色的黑色边线等。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">2. 二维动画难以制作复杂的镜头运动，所以画面大都是平面的，简洁的。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">3. 二维动画画面不像三维画面那么真实，但极富艺术感染力，有着鲜明的个人特质。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.023.png" width="64" height="21" alt=""><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 二维动画与三维动画的区别</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">在动画诞生之初只有动画的概念，并没有二维动画或者三维动画的区别，所以二维动画是在三维动画诞生后才被区分出来的相对概念。这种区别并不是动画效果上的区别——三维动画和二维动画效果其实都是虚拟现实的三维效果，而是制作方式的区别：二维动画采用的是平面画面的制作方式，无论怎样观察，画面的内容不会有任何变化，画面中呈现的物体只有一个面，如图1-10；而三维动画在动画制作软件中是可以三维方式呈现出来的，可以观察到物体的所有面，如图1-11所示。</span></p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; margin-left:0pt"><tbody><tr><td style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.024.png" width="310" height="185" alt=""></p></td><td style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.025.jpeg" width="270" height="193" alt="IMG_256"></p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-10二维动画</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p></td><td style="padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:top"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-11三维动画</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:12pt">&nbsp;</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.018.png" width="23" height="19" alt=""><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 二维动画的制作流程</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">通过网络搜索或查阅资料的方法，再经过分析、归纳和总结后可以得出以下结论：</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">如果以应用领域进行区分，二维动画可以大致分成三种类别，分别有着不同的制作流程。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">1．</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">影视动画片</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">（如图1-12所示）</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.026.jpeg" width="245" height="138" alt="海绵宝宝"></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-12美国电视动画片《海绵宝宝》</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">一般来说，影视动画片的制作流程分为三个阶段：前期设计阶段、中期制作阶段和后期制作阶段。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">前期设计阶段（如图1-13所示）</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.027.png" width="463" height="152" alt="·1"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-13前期设计阶段流程图</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">编写剧本：是制作动画片的第一步，用文字描绘最原始的动画创作蓝图。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">角色设计：依据动画美术风格，设计动画片中出场的角色造型。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">场景设计：依据动画美术风格，设计动画片中的一些重要的场景，侧重角色所处的环境。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">分镜头脚本设计：也称为分镜头台本设计，这是十分重要的过程，主要目的就是把剧本变成可以画面化的方案，给出接下来的制作规划图，里面包含了几乎所有动画制作需要的基本信息，包括每个动画片画面的时间、角色的位置、拍摄的角度等。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">中期制作阶段（如图1-14所示）</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.028.png" width="506" height="124" alt="未命名-2"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-14中期制作阶段流程图</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">分镜头设计稿绘制：动画片的每一个镜头都是由背景和角色两个部分组成的，而背景和角色往往由不同的两组工作人员来完成，所以经常出现完成的背景和角色动画无法很好的融合的问题。绘制分镜头设计稿能够很好解决这一问题，通过确定镜头画面效果来指导二者的制作。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">背景绘制：背景绘制是根据分镜头设计稿中的背景部分绘制成的彩色画稿。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">原画设计：将人物、动物等角色的每一个动作的关键瞬间画面绘制出来的步骤。 </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">动画制作：也称为加动画或加中间画，就是把关键动作之间的中间动作插入补齐。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">后期制作阶段（如图1-15所示）</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.029.png" width="499" height="100" alt="3"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-15后期制作阶段流程图</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">动画上色：就是为完成的角色动画着色。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">音效、音乐制作：为动画片配音，录制音乐。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">合成：将制作完成的一系列动画片的素材组合起来进行再加工。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">剪辑编辑：将合成的素材经过选择、取舍、分解与组接形成符合要求的作品。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">输出成片：在电脑中渲染后导出最终成品。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">2．</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">网络广告动画</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">（如图1-16所示）</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 20pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.030.png" width="218" height="120" alt=""></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-16中国网络广告动画</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 20pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">网络广告动画的制作流程比影视动画片的制作流程更简单，工作环节也较少，如图1-17所示。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.031.png" width="426" height="151" alt="4"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-17制作网络广告动画流程图</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">平面效果图设计：网络广告动画制作的最终效果图。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">分镜头脚本设计：这一步骤和影视动画片类似，区别在于网络广告动画的分镜头脚本（分镜头台本）比较简单，很少有时间长度等信息。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">动画制作：在网络广告动画制作中，这一步骤同时包含了影视动画片中的整个动画成片制作部分，如原画设计与动画制作，上色等。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">素材制作：制作动画所需的素材。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">配合程序输出：动画制作完成后让程序完成交互效果，导出最终成品。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">3．</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">MG动画片</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">（如图1-18所示）</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 20pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.032.png" width="270" height="153" alt=""></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 20pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-18中国MG动画片</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">MG动画片的制作流程（如图1-19所示）</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.033.png" width="419" height="131" alt="5"></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">图1-19 MG动画片制作流程图</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">分镜头脚本设计：同影视动画片的分镜头脚本设计。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">先期配音：先根据分镜头脚本配音，用于配合接下来的动画制作。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">动画制作：同网络广告动画的动画制作。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">素材制作：同网络广告动画的素材制作。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">后期剪辑特效添加：是影视动画片的合成、剪辑编辑的融合。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">输出成片：同影视动画片的输出成片。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.034.png" width="23" height="19" alt=""><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 制作二维动画的相关岗位</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">通过网络搜索资或查阅资料的方法，再经过分析、归纳和总结后可以得出以下结论：</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">三种二维动画的制作流程对应三种不同的二维动画岗位群。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">1．</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">制作影视动画片岗位</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:18.4pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">前期制作阶段的岗位</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">编剧：创作动画剧本，把动画片中出场人物的台词、动作、剧情以文字的形式表现出来。  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">角色设计师：负责动画中角色的造型设计 。 </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">场景设计师：负责动画中的场景设计，并根据每一场戏的要求设计出概念效果图、色彩气氛图。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">分镜师：将剧本画面化，形成分镜头台本，加入电影视觉语言，如镜头运用及摄影角度的变化等强化戏剧的张力。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:18.4pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">中期制作阶段的岗位 </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">背景师：负责根据分镜头设计稿中的背景部分将其绘制成彩色画稿。  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">原画师：负责将分镜头台本中的人物、动物等角色的每一个动作的关键瞬间画面绘制出来。   </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">动画师：动画师是原画师的助手，他的任务是使角色的动作连贯。原画师绘制的原画表现的只是角色的关键动作，因此角色的动作是不连贯的。在这些关键动作之间要将角色的中间动作插入补齐，这就是动画中间画。   </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">后期制作阶段的岗位  </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">特效师：为需要特殊效果的镜头添加光、电等一系列特殊效果。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">合成师：把角色动画、场景、特效、对白、音乐、音效进行合成。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">后期剪辑师：把分散的镜头按照分镜头台本的顺序连接起来，为了进一步加强或减弱某一段落的情节矛盾，将部分镜头进行调整，通过再创作最终达到预期的艺术效果，并渲染输出。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">2．</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> 网络广告动画制作岗位</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">广告美工：确定广告动画要达到的最终平面效果，并为动画师提供动画素材。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">动画师：动画师是整个广告动画的策划和导演，职责是根据广告美工提供的平面广告效果图确定分镜头台本，然后配合程序制作广告动画。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">程序员：根据客户要求配合动画师实现广告的播放。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">3．</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">MG动画片制作岗位</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">动画分镜师：将剧本画面化，形成分镜头台本，构思精巧的动画效果，指导动画师和美工完成工作。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">美工：为每一个镜头绘制场景、角色、道具、特效等素材。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">动画师：配合美工，根据分镜头台本设计制作出每一个镜头的动画效果。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">后期剪辑特效：按照分镜头台本的顺序连接镜头，并将动画镜头进行再加工达到最终的需求效果，并渲染输出。</span></p><p style="line-height:15.6pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.016.png" width="24" height="24" alt="标签集-20"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">拓展练习 </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.017.png" width="23" height="19" alt="标签集-08"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 以下动画中哪几部是二维动画片？（）</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">A 《小猪佩奇》 B《大圣归来》 C《疯狂动物城》 D《你的名字》 E《魔弦传说》</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.018.png" width="23" height="19" alt="标签集-09"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 根据任务所学知识对比二维方向的影视动画片、网络广告动画、MG动画片三种动画的制作流程，说明异同点。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.034.png" width="23" height="19" alt=""><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt"> 根据任务所学知识，说明二维方向的制作影视动画片的岗位，制作网络广告动画的岗位，制作MG动画片的岗位有什么异同点。</span></p><p style="line-height:15.6pt; margin:0pt 18pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9pt">&nbsp;</span><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.035.png" width="192" height="192" alt="" style="margin-left:281.3pt; margin-top:0pt; position:absolute; z-index:-65521"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.036.png" width="192" height="192" alt="" style="margin-left:281.3pt; margin-top:0pt; position:absolute; z-index:-65525"><img src="/conv/5a2a84df249c0/5a2a84df249c0.037.jpeg" width="39" height="39" alt="" style="margin-left:378pt; margin-top:-6.8pt; position:absolute; z-index:-65527"></p></div>
